Name: Should give valid signin details,and proceed to Address Page
Description: After logging in signout button should be displayed,and taken to address page containing 'Addresses' heading and add a new address button.

Name: Authentication Should be required to proceed to CheckOut Process
Description: After the summary page, if the user is not authenticated or logged in , after clicking Proceed to CheckOut button, should prompt appropriate credentials to log into the account to proceed to the next steps of Checkout.Authentication page must contain sign in button.

Name: Order History
Description: After confirmation when user hits back to orders , the user will be taken to page containing the order history and the details of the order.

Name: Confirming order verification
Description: After seeing order summary , when user hits confirm order button, the user will be taken to a page containing Order confirmation and willshow a message of Order being Complete.

Name: Address is changed and updated
Description: Address is given a new value in the address input and Save is clicked and address update is verified

Name: Mandatory Fields Must be filled up for successful sign up
Confirm Order button is checked
Description: After choosing payment by bankwire,Confirm order button is verified whether it is present or not and whether correct payment option is selected or not.

Name: Terms of service checked and proceeded to payment
Description: After checking the terms of service, Payment Checkout Page will appear which will have subheading of choosing paymemnt options

Name: Firstname and lastname cannot include any digit at last
Description: User cannot give firstname and last name containing digits, should contain only alphabets,numbers can be in between the alphabets.

Name: User can see product summary
Description: User can view product summary before checkout

Name: After giving valid email,user will be redirecrted to registration form
Address Update Button Clicked and taken to a address change form
Description: After clicking billing address update button,it should be taken to a address update form page where there will be 'Your Addresses' subheadingand a Save button below the form

Name: proceedToCheckOutButton
Description: After searching a dress, adding to cart being operated correctly or not is verified,Proceed to checkout button is present or not is verified and clicked.

Name: Zip/postal code must not be more or less than five digits
Delivery Address and billing address should contain update option
Description: Billing address and Delivery address should contain Update Option below them

Name: Terms of Service is Unchecked
Description: Without agreeing terms of service user cannot proceed to payment,will give prompt to agree it before continuing.

Name: Cannot Create Account with already registered email
Invalid Password Given,must be minimum 5 length
User can add cart successfully
Description: User added the product into card

Name: User can choose product
Description: User can choose product from the product list

Name: Available Payment Options
Description: Two payment options should be available in the payment page:bankWire and Cheque

Name: User press register button without inputting any data
Should proceed to Shipping Page containing Terms of service
Description: After proceeding to checkout further, it should be headed to Shipping Page containing Terms of Service.
